<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti saka<unclear>varṣa</unclear> 963 neya viṣasaṁvatsarada <unclear>jyēṣṭa</unclear>
<lb n="2"/>bahuḷa 8 mi Ādityavāradandu śrīmat<unclear>go</unclear>
<lb n="3" break="no"/>mmarasara<unclear>ṇu</unclear>gi boḷḷabbe tanna<unclear>dē</unclear>
<lb n="4" break="no"/>gulakke koṭṭa sundari<unclear>ya</unclear>kalla teṁ
<lb n="5" break="no"/>kadeseya keymatta 50 tōṇṭa 1 A<unclear>yva</unclear>
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ttu maneya nēsaṇamida
<lb n="7" break="no"/>rkkaruhar candrasēkarabhaṭārarī
<lb n="8"/>bhūmiyaṁ gommarasar bo
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ḷḷabbege dharmaṁ geyyendudaya
<lb n="10" break="no"/>geydarī sthānavaṁ sēguṇa
<lb n="11" break="no"/>ra vaṁsadoḷārarasugeydoḍaṁ
<lb n="12"/>pratipāḷisuvudu <g type="ddanda">.</g> 
</p>

